<template>
    <button
    class="btn btn-danger btn-sm ml-1"
    v-on:click="deleteSubscription(subscription)">
    Delete
    </button>
</template>

<script lang="ts">
import axios from 'axios';
import Vue from 'vue'
export default Vue.extend({
    data() {
        return {
            subscriptions: []
        }
    },
    methods:{
        all: function () {
        axios.get('http://127.0.0.1:8000/ciclo_de_vida/')
            .then( response => {
                this.subscriptions = response.data
            });
    },

    created() {
        this.all();
    },

    deleteSubscription: function(subscr) {
    if (confirm('Delete ' + subscr.versao)) {
        axios.delete(`http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/ciclo_de_vida/${subscr.id}`)
            .then( response => {
                this.all();
            });
    }
},
    }    
})
</script>
